OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bill
OL,4,CJohnston
OL,6,FBill Johnston, Age 100, Royal Field
OL,7,FArtillery
OL,9,FInterviewed 20 Nov 2023
OL,11,FDied 16 August 2024
OL,13,FA driver and wireless operator with a
OL,14,Fgun crew, Bill Johnston landed on Gold
OL,15,FBeach on D-Day in the back of a half
OL,16,Ftrack - a truck with wheels on the
OL,17,Ffront and tracks in the back.
OL,19,FHe'd crossed the Channel from
OL,20,FBournemouth in a Tank Landing Craft
OL,21,Fwith gun crews.
