OL,4,CJohnston
OL,6,F25 pounder guns mounted on a Sherman
OL,7,Ftank chassis and fired barrages on
OL,8,Fenemy positions and targeted enemy
OL,9,Ftanks.
OL,11,FHe said: "I obviously didn't know it
OL,12,Fwas D-Day. It wasn't talked about. It
OL,13,Fwas a fairly quiet run-in until we got
OL,14,Fwithin range as it were.
OL,16,F"Our guns in the welldeck were firing
OL,17,Fat targets ashore and there was
OL,18,Fincoming
