OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bill
OL,4,CJohnston
OL,6,FMr Johnston remembers being involved
OL,7,Fin action and another gun crew
OL,8,Fknocking out Panzer tanks as they
OL,9,Fmoved forward.
OL,11,FHe and the crews would receive targets
OL,12,Fand pass it onto the gun crews.
OL,14,F"Often times I would drive to spot
OL,15,Ftargets, spot the shots and on one
OL,16,Foccasion we formed a creeping barrage.
OL,17,FWith the infantry sheltering behind us
OL,18,Funtil we could get no further and they
OL,19,Fcame past us.
