OL,6,F"I was in a Sherman tank at this time
OL,7,Fas a wireless operator."
OL,9,FIn September he was fired upon while
OL,10,Fdriving a jeep, wounded and later
OL,11,Fdischarged.
OL,13,FHe said: "A shell landed nearby and I
OL,14,Fwas driving a jeep at the time and
OL,15,Fdived into a ditch.
